# Flip multiverse API (Phase 1)

## Required

```env
FLIP_TOKEN_ENCRYPTION_KEY=change-me-to-a-random-string-at-least-32-chars
```

## Optional

```env
FLIP_API_PORT=8788
FLIP_DB_PATH=./data/flip-multiverse.db
FLIP_DELIVERY_MAX_ATTEMPTS=5
FLIP_DELIVERY_BACKOFF_BASE_MS=60000
FLIP_DELIVERY_BACKOFF_CAP_MS=900000
PORT=8788
```

## Client (Expo)

```env
EXPO_PUBLIC_FLIP_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8788
```

On a physical Android device, use your PC LAN IP or `adb reverse tcp:8788 tcp:8788`.
